IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: LIST OF ATTACHMENTS: 1. Copy of NCMEC Cybertip 174805363 ACTION TAKEN: On November 30, 2023, Cpl. Heid began an investigation into NCMEC Cyberip 174805363. The tip was sent to NCMEC from Snapchat about user cm39773 soliciting sex and/or sexual images from what appears to be a juvenile female. Snapchat provided the following information: Incident Information Primary Incident Type: Online Enticement of Children for Sexual Acts Incident Time: 09-24-2023 10:56:17 UTC Child Victim Date of Birth: 12-22-2009 Email Address: mel52770@hotmail.com Screen/User Name: gracie16385 IP Address: 69.255.143.178 (Login) 09-23-2023 13:37:44 UTC Additional Information: The account identifier provided is a username which should be provided when seeking data. Suspect Date of Birth: 10-07-2000 Email Address: lennybrown1995@gmail.com Screen/User Name: cm39773 IP Address: 73.86.61.232 (Login) 09-20-2023 05:46:43 UTC Snapchat further provided the following text: account.cm39773 2023-08-21T18:43:06.859Z: I will kiss you in between your legs gracie16385 2023-08-21T18:42:39.496Z: Yes? cm39773 2023-08-21T18:42:23.421Z: Babyyyy cm39773 2023-08-21T18:40:51.626Z: I love you cm39773 2023-08-21T18:39:58.599Z: gracie16385 2023-08-21T18:39:43.646Z: No cm39773 2023-08-21T18:39:28.193Z: Take them off gracie16385 2023-08-21T18:38:59.356Z: Yes A check of the suspect IP address resolved to Comcast with a geo-location of Elkton, MD. A check of the potential child victims IP address also resolved to Comcast with a geo-location of Pasadena, MD. Cpl. Heid authored a subpoena to the Anne Arundel County States Attorneys Office for Comcast and will be awaiting its return. The case will remain open at this time. CASE OPEN
